<appendix id="installation">
<title>Installation</title>

<sect1 id="getting-kapp">
<title>How to obtain &aki;</title>

<sect2 id="getting-kapp-lib">
<title>Obtain and build <acronym>IRC</acronym> library</title>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry><term>Requirements</term>
<listitem><para>&kde; 4.3 or newer</para>
<para>PyQt4</para>
<para>PyKDE4</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>List of changes for &aki; <acronym>IRC</acronym> Library</term>
<listitem>
<para>
You can find a list of changes for the &aki; <acronym>IRC</acronym> Library at
<ulink url="http://www.gitorious.org/aki/akiirc/commits"/>.
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>Build &aki; <acronym>IRC</acronym> Library</term>
<listitem>
<para>
In &konsole; or your preferred terminal application, issue the following
commands:
<screen>
git clone git://gitorious.org/aki/akiirc.git
cd akiirc
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=debugfull -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path
make
sudo make install
</screen>
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="getting-kapp-app">
<title>Obtain and build &aki;</title>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry><term>Requirements</term>
<listitem><para><link linkend="getting-kapp-lib">&aki; <acronym>IRC</acronym>
Library</link></para>
<para>&kde; 4.3 or newer</para>
<para>PyQt4</para>
<para>PyKDE4</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>List of changes for &aki;</term>
<listitem>
<para>
You can find a list of changes for &aki; at <ulink
url="http://www.gitorious.org/aki/aki/commits"/>.
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>Build &aki;</term>
<listitem>
<para>
In &konsole; or your preferred terminal application, issue the following
commands:
<screen>
git clone git://gitorious.org/aki/aki.git
cd aki
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=debugfull -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path
make
sudo make install
</screen>
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</sect2>
</sect1>

